1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 19]

2
00:00:19,370 --> 00:00:20,209
What happened?

3
00:00:20,610 --> 00:00:21,609
How did things change so suddenly?

4
00:00:22,250 --> 00:00:22,969
I'm tired.

5
00:00:23,730 --> 00:00:24,529
I don't want to fight anymore.

6
00:00:26,250 --> 00:00:27,129
And I'm outmatched.

7
00:00:27,850 --> 00:00:29,209
How could you be outmatched?

8
00:00:29,610 --> 00:00:30,409
Last night,

9
00:00:30,570 --> 00:00:32,849
I visited every elder in your place.

10
00:00:32,850 --> 00:00:34,009
I handled everything for you.

11
00:00:34,370 --> 00:00:35,809
Did Zhou Yimo threaten you?

12
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:36,889
If so,

13
00:00:37,090 --> 00:00:38,089
I'll teach him a lesson for you.

14
00:00:38,730 --> 00:00:39,609
Zhou Quan.

15
00:00:39,970 --> 00:00:41,289
I really don't want to compete anymore.

16
00:00:41,570 --> 00:00:42,809
Don't push me, okay?

17
00:00:44,930 --> 00:00:45,769
I can't accept this.

18
00:00:47,730 --> 00:00:48,609
You won't accept it?

19
00:00:48,970 --> 00:00:50,209
You have a family.

20
00:00:50,690 --> 00:00:53,009
I'm your cousin's lawful wife.

21
00:00:54,010 --> 00:00:55,049
Our relationship

22
00:00:55,330 --> 00:00:56,849
must remain hidden forever.

23
00:00:57,730 --> 00:00:58,489
So

24
00:00:58,850 --> 00:01:00,609
forgive me for thinking more

25
00:01:00,850 --> 00:01:02,209
about myself and my child.

26
00:01:03,250 --> 00:01:04,489
But I can't bear to let go.

27
00:01:07,490 --> 00:01:08,329
If you can't bear it,

28
00:01:09,210 --> 00:01:10,729
then come visit us in the city more often.

29
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:12,849
I'll prepare the finest tea for you.

30
00:01:21,090 --> 00:01:22,529
The Zhou family's businesses are complex.

31
00:01:22,970 --> 00:01:24,769
To fully return to the He family

32
00:01:25,770 --> 00:01:27,169
will take some time.

33
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:29,569
It seems you're determined to change

34
00:01:29,770 --> 00:01:31,689
the Zhou residence to the He residence.

35
00:01:36,130 --> 00:01:37,169
The ceremony is about to begin.

36
00:01:37,570 --> 00:01:38,729
What are you doing?

37
00:01:39,650 --> 00:01:40,689
What did you just call me?

38
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:41,809
Young master.

39
00:01:43,970 --> 00:01:44,969
Zhou Yimo, what are you doing?

40
00:01:47,050 --> 00:01:48,169
Still not changing how you address me?

41
00:01:50,650 --> 00:01:51,409
Master.

42
00:01:58,610 --> 00:01:59,449
I promised you

43
00:02:00,010 --> 00:02:01,569
the first thing I'd do as the Master

44
00:02:01,810 --> 00:02:03,369
is restore your freedom.

45
00:02:07,650 --> 00:02:08,729
I can't leave yet.

46
00:02:09,250 --> 00:02:10,249
I must stay at the Zhou residence

47
00:02:10,650 --> 00:02:11,529
to find the real murderer.

48
00:02:11,650 --> 00:02:12,649
With your freedom restored,

49
00:02:12,810 --> 00:02:14,209
you can still investigate the murder.

50
00:02:14,730 --> 00:02:15,289
I'm sick

51
00:02:15,290 --> 00:02:16,689
of calling you "fifth concubine" every day.

52
00:02:16,770 --> 00:02:17,489
That won't do.

53
00:02:18,010 --> 00:02:18,969
Without my status,

54
00:02:19,290 --> 00:02:20,689
what reason do I have to stay?

55
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:21,529
I'll marry you.

56
00:02:24,050 --> 00:02:25,289
Be my wife.

57
00:02:25,770 --> 00:02:26,289
Will you?

58
00:02:28,770 --> 00:02:29,489
Zhou Yimo.

59
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:31,009
Marriage is a serious matter.

60
00:02:31,570 --> 00:02:32,409
It's not a joke.

61
00:02:33,170 --> 00:02:34,769
Especially in these chaotic times.

62
00:02:35,930 --> 00:02:37,009
With your position,

63
00:02:37,290 --> 00:02:37,969
you should find someone

64
00:02:37,970 --> 00:02:39,449
who can assist you in your career

65
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:40,649
and benefit mutually.

66
00:02:41,770 --> 00:02:43,529
I live only for revenge.

67
00:02:44,050 --> 00:02:44,969
I'm no good match.

68
00:02:46,450 --> 00:02:47,289
Your excuses

69
00:02:47,770 --> 00:02:49,809
for backing out sound so righteous.

70
00:02:50,330 --> 00:02:51,249
You know perfectly well

71
00:02:51,450 --> 00:02:52,449
I must have you.

72
00:02:59,050 --> 00:02:59,769
Master.

73
00:02:59,930 --> 00:03:01,409
All the clan elders are waiting for you.

74
00:03:01,810 --> 00:03:02,769
Don't miss the appointed time.

75
00:03:12,890 --> 00:03:13,929
Then I'll wait for you.

76
00:03:14,490 --> 00:03:15,129
Waiting for you

77
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,329
to succeed in your revenge.

78
00:03:21,490 --> 00:03:24,009
Now invite Zhou Yimo, the new head of the Zhou family,

79
00:03:24,250 --> 00:03:25,769
along with family and friends,

80
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:28,089
to offer incense to our ancestors.

81
00:03:35,410 --> 00:03:36,409
First bow.

82
00:03:40,850 --> 00:03:42,049
Second bow.

83
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:44,489
All suspects have been ruled out.

84
00:03:45,050 --> 00:03:47,049
Only the "Rogue Tears" remains as a clue.

85
00:03:47,930 --> 00:03:49,409
Third bow - The "Rogue Tears" in sister's hand -

86
00:03:50,130 --> 00:03:51,329
whose is it?

87
00:03:51,530 --> 00:03:52,169
Fifth Concubine.

88
00:03:52,530 --> 00:03:53,569
Why are you here?

89
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:55,969
Fourth bow.

90
00:03:56,930 --> 00:03:57,609
Nanxi.

91
00:03:58,170 --> 00:03:59,369
You told me that

92
00:03:59,810 --> 00:04:00,729
"Rogue Tears" was an exclusive

93
00:04:00,770 --> 00:04:03,009
luxury rouge for the Second Concubine.

94
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:05,169
But that day I clearly saw

95
00:04:05,170 --> 00:04:06,169
the Fourth Concubine

96
00:04:06,170 --> 00:04:07,689
also asking the steward for it.

97
00:04:07,690 --> 00:04:09,529
When the Second Concubine was still here

98
00:04:09,530 --> 00:04:10,649
she managed it very strictly.

99
00:04:11,130 --> 00:04:11,929
This "Rogue Tears"

100
00:04:12,170 --> 00:04:13,769
had to be made exclusively for her.

101
00:04:14,250 --> 00:04:15,329
What's so special

102
00:04:15,850 --> 00:04:17,289
about this "Rogue Tears"?

103
00:04:17,570 --> 00:04:19,129
I heard it has a secret formula

104
00:04:19,410 --> 00:04:20,409
that keeps the rouge

105
00:04:20,410 --> 00:04:21,929
bright and fresh for a long time.

106
00:04:22,170 --> 00:04:23,689
It doesn't stain cups or fade.

107
00:04:23,890 --> 00:04:25,089
Truly miraculous.

108
00:04:25,210 --> 00:04:25,769
So does that mean

109
00:04:25,770 --> 00:04:27,329
I could also get "Rogue Tears"?

110
00:04:27,490 --> 00:04:28,649
The person who makes "Rogue Tears"

111
00:04:28,650 --> 00:04:30,489
can only be contacted through the steward.

112
00:04:30,930 --> 00:04:32,249
The steward belongs to the Fourth Concubine.

113
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:32,969
So...

114
00:04:32,970 --> 00:04:33,849
The steward

115
00:04:33,850 --> 00:04:34,889
would definitely find a way

116
00:04:34,890 --> 00:04:36,329
to arrange its production for her.

117
00:04:36,650 --> 00:04:38,009
But for you, it's difficult.

118
00:04:40,930 --> 00:04:43,049
Only the steward can contact them.

119
00:04:43,970 --> 00:04:44,849
This is specially

120
00:04:44,850 --> 00:04:46,449
custom-made "Rogue Tears" for you.

121
00:04:51,810 --> 00:04:53,009
Only three boxes?

122
00:04:54,050 --> 00:04:55,409
Can't you get more?

123
00:04:55,650 --> 00:04:56,369
Ms. Lin.

124
00:04:56,690 --> 00:04:57,569
You know

125
00:04:58,170 --> 00:04:59,729
the production process for "Rogue Tears"

126
00:04:59,930 --> 00:05:00,969
is extremely complicated.

127
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:02,929
Now that the Second Concubine and Master are dead,

128
00:05:03,890 --> 00:05:05,169
what are you worried about?

129
00:05:07,210 --> 00:05:08,529
Do I not even have

130
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:10,649
this little privilege with you?

131
00:05:11,650 --> 00:05:13,249
Get me some more.

132
00:05:13,690 --> 00:05:15,449
I'm leaving tomorrow.

133
00:05:20,770 --> 00:05:21,289
Fine.

134
00:05:21,970 --> 00:05:23,169
I'll prepare it right away.

135
00:06:45,330 --> 00:06:46,249
Fifth Concubine.

136
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:48,689
When did you arrive?

137
00:06:49,010 --> 00:06:49,969
Steward Xu?

138
00:06:50,850 --> 00:06:52,529
What did you see?

139
00:06:54,690 --> 00:06:55,929
You followed me!

140
00:06:56,690 --> 00:06:58,489
You just want "Rogue Tears," right?

141
00:06:59,970 --> 00:07:00,689
Fine.

142
00:07:01,490 --> 00:07:02,569
I'll tell you.

143
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:04,169
"Rogue Tears"

144
00:07:04,490 --> 00:07:06,569
requires a special ingredient.

145
00:07:09,690 --> 00:07:12,169
The blood of young maidens.

146
00:07:14,690 --> 00:07:15,569
Fifth Concubine.

147
00:07:16,970 --> 00:07:17,849
I know the Master never

148
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:20,969
laid a hand on you.

149
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:23,729
So you're still fit to

150
00:07:24,170 --> 00:07:26,489
serve as an ingredient.

151
00:07:42,730 --> 00:07:45,249
All the inspiration for making Rogue Tears

152
00:07:45,810 --> 00:07:47,529
came from this.

153
00:07:51,850 --> 00:07:52,809
Indeed,

154
00:07:53,410 --> 00:07:55,089
a maiden's blood

155
00:07:56,210 --> 00:07:58,489
is so sweetly fragrant.

156
00:08:04,690 --> 00:08:05,409
Where is she?

157
00:08:05,570 --> 00:08:06,409
Have you found her?

158
00:08:07,010 --> 00:08:07,689
Everyone's been questioned.

159
00:08:07,690 --> 00:08:09,049
She didn't leave the mansion tonight.

160
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:11,209
Master,

161
00:08:11,330 --> 00:08:12,569
she disappeared inside the mansion.

162
00:08:12,570 --> 00:08:14,129
Could it really be haunted?

163
00:08:14,130 --> 00:08:14,769
Find out

164
00:08:14,770 --> 00:08:16,289
who's missing in the mansion.

165
00:08:16,410 --> 00:08:17,969
Send everyone to search for Ye Zhiqiu.

166
00:08:17,970 --> 00:08:19,129
Leave no corner unchecked.

167
00:08:19,130 --> 00:08:19,529
Yes!

168
00:08:19,530 --> 00:08:20,689
I'll search outside.

169
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:21,249
Let's go.

170
00:08:21,610 --> 00:08:22,609
Fifth concubine,

171
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:25,009
look.

172
00:08:26,130 --> 00:08:27,969
This is your Rogue Tears.

173
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:32,289
But I'm afraid...

174
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:34,289
you won't be needing it anymore.

175
00:08:42,130 --> 00:08:42,849
Steward Xu,

176
00:08:44,210 --> 00:08:45,409
I have no quarrel with you.

177
00:08:46,290 --> 00:08:47,089
Just because I know

178
00:08:47,090 --> 00:08:48,489
you made Rogue Tears,

179
00:08:48,970 --> 00:08:50,129
you want to kill me?

180
00:08:51,410 --> 00:08:52,929
No quarrel?

181
00:08:54,410 --> 00:08:56,129
If not for your meddling,

182
00:08:56,770 --> 00:08:57,529
would Ms. Lin

183
00:08:57,530 --> 00:08:58,729
have withdrawn from the campaign?

184
00:09:02,730 --> 00:09:03,449
Steward Xu,

185
00:09:05,290 --> 00:09:06,449
after toiling half your life,

186
00:09:07,090 --> 00:09:09,289
having so many men father your child,

187
00:09:09,610 --> 00:09:11,009
you must be quite content, no?

188
00:09:13,130 --> 00:09:14,009
Fifth concubine,

189
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:17,129
I don't understand what you mean.

190
00:09:17,770 --> 00:09:19,209
Ms. Yinan's color blindness

191
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:20,809
is inherited from you, isn't it?

192
00:09:21,810 --> 00:09:23,089
On the day of the master's funeral,

193
00:09:23,450 --> 00:09:24,609
I discovered your

194
00:09:24,610 --> 00:09:26,449
long-hidden eye condition.

195
00:09:34,330 --> 00:09:35,849
I didn't reveal the truth

196
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:37,569
to preserve some dignity

197
00:09:37,570 --> 00:09:39,009
for your family of four.

198
00:09:44,930 --> 00:09:45,769
Fifth concubine,

199
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:47,929
you are clever,

200
00:09:48,770 --> 00:09:51,049
but sometimes cleverness backfires.

201
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:52,689
You know that?

202
00:10:19,050 --> 00:10:20,049
Rogue Tears

203
00:10:20,330 --> 00:10:22,409
requires a special ingredient:

204
00:10:23,570 --> 00:10:25,889
the blood of young maidens.

205
00:10:30,730 --> 00:10:31,489
So much...

206
00:10:32,570 --> 00:10:33,329
All these

207
00:10:34,170 --> 00:10:35,849
are made with girls' blood.

208
00:10:36,730 --> 00:10:41,489
[Ye Chuxue]

209
00:11:01,850 --> 00:11:02,849
Sister!

210
00:11:08,330 --> 00:11:09,209
What are you doing?

211
00:11:09,930 --> 00:11:10,289
Stop!

212
00:11:10,650 --> 00:11:11,449
Don't touch them!

213
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:13,089
Fifth concubine,

214
00:11:13,370 --> 00:11:14,689
that's my life's work.

215
00:11:14,850 --> 00:11:16,529
Don't touch them! I can explain!

216
00:11:22,370 --> 00:11:23,209
Explain?

217
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:25,769
Then answer me:

218
00:11:26,650 --> 00:11:27,369
Who is this?

219
00:11:28,410 --> 00:11:29,729
What did you do to her?

220
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:33,729
On New Year's Eve three years ago,

221
00:11:34,490 --> 00:11:36,209
after escorting the Fourth concubine back to town,

222
00:11:36,210 --> 00:11:37,409
you returned to the mansion.

223
00:11:37,890 --> 00:11:39,969
No one found your whereabouts suspicious.

224
00:11:40,090 --> 00:11:41,249
But deep down,

225
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:42,809
you knew what you did.

226
00:11:46,010 --> 00:11:46,969
I don't know.

227
00:11:47,410 --> 00:11:48,209
You don't know?

228
00:11:51,170 --> 00:11:51,969
You don't know?

229
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:52,889
Stop it!

230
00:11:56,770 --> 00:11:57,649
Talk!

231
00:11:57,890 --> 00:11:58,969
What did you do to her?

232
00:12:00,330 --> 00:12:01,289
Are you talking or not?

233
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:04,609
Stop it, Ye Zhiqiu!

234
00:12:11,490 --> 00:12:12,569
I'll talk.

235
00:12:15,170 --> 00:12:16,049
I'll talk.

236
00:12:18,690 --> 00:12:19,729
Three years ago,

237
00:12:20,890 --> 00:12:23,409
Chuxue wrote to meet me in the backyard.

238
00:12:24,890 --> 00:12:25,809
At first,

239
00:12:28,050 --> 00:12:29,729
I truly didn't mean to hurt her.

240
00:12:30,890 --> 00:12:33,009
[On New Year's Eve three years ago]

241
00:12:46,450 --> 00:12:48,729
Why call me at this late hour?

242
00:12:51,770 --> 00:12:52,849
Help me!

243
00:12:53,970 --> 00:12:54,689
Chuxue?

244
00:12:55,970 --> 00:12:56,849
What's wrong?

245
00:13:03,250 --> 00:13:04,729
Steward, help me!

246
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:17,129
Chuxue!

247
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:20,289
You're bleeding so much!

248
00:13:46,050 --> 00:13:46,929
So

249
00:13:48,690 --> 00:13:50,809
the Rogue Tears were left by you.

250
00:13:53,290 --> 00:13:54,609
And the one who assaulted her

251
00:13:56,050 --> 00:13:57,169
was also you.

252
00:13:58,450 --> 00:13:59,209
Yes.

253
00:14:00,450 --> 00:14:01,649
I did it all.

254
00:14:02,970 --> 00:14:04,809
But she invited me.

255
00:14:05,690 --> 00:14:07,169
If she hadn't seduced me,

256
00:14:07,730 --> 00:14:09,529
I wouldn't have touched her.

257
00:14:09,530 --> 00:14:10,449
Bullshit!

258
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:12,089
She's not like that.

259
00:14:18,890 --> 00:14:19,649
Xu Hansheng.

260
00:14:24,210 --> 00:14:25,849
Your secret is exposed.

261
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:30,969
You can't hide your identity anymore.

262
00:14:31,930 --> 00:14:33,689
I'll strangle you!

263
00:14:36,250 --> 00:14:38,129
The tighter you choke me, the sooner you'll pass out.

264
00:14:38,330 --> 00:14:40,009
I drugged you.

265
00:14:52,410 --> 00:14:53,769
After all this circling around,

266
00:14:55,090 --> 00:14:56,329
it was him.

267
00:15:11,610 --> 00:15:12,329
Awake?

268
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:15,969
How long was I out?

269
00:15:17,370 --> 00:15:18,129
Three days.

270
00:15:21,410 --> 00:15:22,209
The Steward?

271
00:15:22,730 --> 00:15:23,609
Where is he?

272
00:15:26,450 --> 00:15:27,329
Still in the mansion.

273
00:15:28,490 --> 00:15:30,449
Why not send him to the police station?

274
00:15:30,810 --> 00:15:32,089
No solid evidence

275
00:15:32,210 --> 00:15:33,129
to convict him.

276
00:15:33,130 --> 00:15:33,689
Then

277
00:15:35,090 --> 00:15:36,449
those Rogue Tears,

278
00:15:37,010 --> 00:15:37,729
those Rogue Tears

279
00:15:37,730 --> 00:15:39,049
are made from girls' blood.

280
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:41,729
Each bottle has a name on it.

281
00:15:42,330 --> 00:15:44,009
There must be other victims.

282
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:45,609
But these girls didn't die.

283
00:15:46,010 --> 00:15:46,769
The Steward said

284
00:15:47,490 --> 00:15:48,609
they were custom-made

285
00:15:48,770 --> 00:15:50,009
so the names were marked.

286
00:15:50,410 --> 00:15:51,569
Custom-made or not,

287
00:15:52,330 --> 00:15:53,209
we can easily find out.

288
00:15:53,650 --> 00:15:54,489
I had someone

289
00:15:54,490 --> 00:15:55,729
investigate discreetly.

290
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:56,489
Look.

291
00:15:56,770 --> 00:15:58,489
Xu Hansheng's real name is Xu Jiaxuan.

292
00:15:58,810 --> 00:16:01,009
He previously worked at Fourth Concubine's family's rouge shop.

293
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:02,489
Fifteen years ago,

294
00:16:02,650 --> 00:16:04,249
he was a Chinese teacher at a girls' school.

295
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:07,649
Later, he was reported by parents for seducing female students

296
00:16:07,730 --> 00:16:08,689
and was eventually dismissed.

297
00:16:09,050 --> 00:16:10,089
But there was no evidence,

298
00:16:10,250 --> 00:16:11,009
so he couldn't be convicted.

299
00:16:11,850 --> 00:16:12,689
Except for Chuxue,

300
00:16:13,210 --> 00:16:14,449
everyone marked on the Rouge Tears

301
00:16:14,610 --> 00:16:15,969
graduated from that girls' school.

302
00:16:16,290 --> 00:16:17,809
If I'm not mistaken,

303
00:16:18,570 --> 00:16:19,369
they were all the students

304
00:16:19,370 --> 00:16:20,649
he took advantage of back then.

305
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:22,809
The blood of these girls

306
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:25,209
was likely taken when he seduced them,

307
00:16:25,490 --> 00:16:27,489
against their will.

308
00:16:29,730 --> 00:16:30,489
Where are you going?

309
00:16:30,490 --> 00:16:31,689
I'm going to find those girls.

310
00:16:32,330 --> 00:16:33,889
If it was seduction,

311
00:16:34,090 --> 00:16:34,969
they must know...

312
00:16:34,970 --> 00:16:35,809
We can't

313
00:16:36,650 --> 00:16:38,289
panic now.

314
00:16:40,610 --> 00:16:41,329
Zhou Yimo,

315
00:16:42,970 --> 00:16:43,769
help me.

316
00:16:44,250 --> 00:16:46,489
Find me the best lawyer in town.

317
00:16:47,730 --> 00:16:48,489
For what?

318
00:16:49,370 --> 00:16:50,129
This time,

319
00:16:51,330 --> 00:16:52,649
I won't let him escape.

320
00:16:54,290 --> 00:16:54,889
Okay.

321
00:17:02,410 --> 00:17:03,929
Fifth Concubine, you're quite persistent.

322
00:17:05,370 --> 00:17:06,929
Why are you so determined to pursue me?

323
00:17:09,730 --> 00:17:11,049
Now that the master is dead,

324
00:17:12,090 --> 00:17:13,569
this secret doesn't matter.

325
00:17:16,290 --> 00:17:17,729
I'm Ye Chuxue's sister.

326
00:17:17,930 --> 00:17:18,849
What?

327
00:17:19,210 --> 00:17:21,729
You should pay for what you've done.

328
00:17:23,770 --> 00:17:24,889
I didn't kill her.

329
00:17:25,410 --> 00:17:26,209
Besides,

330
00:17:26,650 --> 00:17:28,209
you have no evidence

331
00:17:28,330 --> 00:17:29,529
that I assaulted her.

332
00:17:30,170 --> 00:17:31,289
But someone will

333
00:17:31,850 --> 00:17:34,009
accuse you of your crimes.

334
00:17:35,050 --> 00:17:36,289
You mean...

335
00:17:37,090 --> 00:17:39,209
those girls marked on the Rouge Tears?

336
00:17:41,650 --> 00:17:42,169
Yes.

337
00:17:42,730 --> 00:17:43,969
I used their blood

338
00:17:44,610 --> 00:17:46,649
to make the most expensive rouge.

339
00:17:47,850 --> 00:17:49,569
And I gave them the most precious memory

340
00:17:49,730 --> 00:17:51,289
of their youth.

341
00:17:52,250 --> 00:17:54,289
I let them experience the joy of love.

342
00:17:54,570 --> 00:17:56,089
They should thank me, shouldn't they?

343
00:17:57,570 --> 00:17:58,449
Now,

344
00:17:59,410 --> 00:18:01,289
they're all married women.

345
00:18:02,250 --> 00:18:03,449
They can't bear

346
00:18:03,890 --> 00:18:05,529
the gossip they'd face

347
00:18:05,650 --> 00:18:07,089
after accusing me.

348
00:18:08,450 --> 00:18:09,169
Fifth Concubine,

349
00:18:09,850 --> 00:18:11,009
let me be honest.

350
00:18:11,370 --> 00:18:12,969
You can't win against me.

351
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:16,649
Xu Hansheng,

352
00:18:18,250 --> 00:18:19,409
we'll see about that.

353
00:18:20,770 --> 00:18:21,369
Fine.

354
00:18:22,410 --> 00:18:23,249
I'll be waiting.
